pageContext.claim: “New Strzok-Page texts reveal ‘Media Leak Strategy.’  @FoxNews  So terrible, and NOTHING is being done at DOJ or FBI - but the world is watching, and they get it completely.”
pageContext.analysis: This tweet neatly illustrates the risk of getting distorted information from Fox News. The term "media leak strategy" in text messages between Peter Strzok and Lisa Page of the FBI had nothing to do with disseminating leaks but with preventing them.
